    {
        "content": "<p>Problems:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>hard coded dynamic library name</li>\n<li>hard coded where to find dynamic library</li>\n<li>hard coded linker name</li>\n<li>hard coded linker arguments</li>\n</ul>",
